    { "_comment": "One residential face covers the entire 4×2 grid; ribbon-union clip carves all streets out automatically. Ring extends well past chain reach on every side (chains end ≤ ±150 in x and ≤ ±70 in z + ~7m ribbon outer ≈ ±157 / ±77 worst case) so no inner-edge can fall inside any ribbon outer.",
